i\" /> （冇買咩特別野）</blockquote><br />\n咁扣左啲水上活動仲淨返幾多錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未預到用幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  btw 我預多因為我同條女會狂食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 早午晚便利店宵夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以15000 係for 2個人定 每人$15000？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩人呀</blockquote><br />\n唔買手信應該ok ，一日三餐，平平地兩個3000円一餐，14日都要12萬yen 加埋交通應該差唔多，你仲要沖繩去福岡呢⋯⋯</blockquote><br />\n計哂交通住宿 15000淨係食同玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  福岡去沖繩搭ana 想去百合之濱</blockquote><br />\n百合之濱真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上年4月去過不過要夾岩退潮時間<br />\n同埋個島都無咩好玩好食又細 係來回個島最貴<br />\n不過十分值得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c341d58e30082d8c0d96dfc673b7b33cf9af5ba4","tid":387660,"uid":122684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T01:17:41.000Z","msg":"如果萬五蚊2個人，6日夠唔夠"},{"pid":"2d32595ec044ebae3e70d64d40d3305e06edeeba","tid":387660,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T01:18:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d0a962df9dd50d3d14b3747c55a7d6568ef91001","tid":387660,"uid":281,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T01:19:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6fba41a2b2f184bfa8244e88a32cbee19e10bb47","tid":387660,"uid":82398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T03:58:04.000Z","msg":"十幾日 有咩事上黎就收得皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d98c690b86b68e2a8ab6481fb8f36db390c2ae9","tid":387660,"uid":34080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T04:02:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0528842f790935bd425eec7740a9c85fbe579a7","tid":387660,"uid":34080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T04:03:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3313f9cbb55e4621fb65ad38630ea9d889cae638","tid":387660,"uid":1473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T04:53:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果萬五蚊2個人，6日夠唔夠</blockquote><br />\n淨食同交通都ok 既，買野就簽卡啦，<br />\n日本食野基本都1000円起標，地鐵/jr/巴士 亦都貴過港鐵"},{"pid":"3ec3621f9e8565ce50c7aeb5b13d5601a2518b49","tid":387660,"uid":37942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T04:54:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果萬五蚊2個人，6日夠唔夠</blockquote><br />\n淨食同交通都ok 既，買野就簽卡啦，<br />\n日本食野基本都1000円起標，地鐵/jr/巴士 亦都貴過港鐵</blockquote><br />\n買三日卷啦"},{"pid":"86c53e14c6fc7b917287448d46b38fe4f9c4de33","tid":387660,"uid":32391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T05:05:25.000Z","msg":"冇5萬都唔敢去"},{"pid":"dea386cb14057c7dadc48e1f9fa01a5198b0d27a","tid":387660,"uid":2671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T05:18:42.000Z","msg":"2個人至少預4萬5"},{"pid":"a0892fe5a578e81923fd9973288fe3905adb1374","tid":387660,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T05:24:01.000Z","msg":"夠有突啦 上次去 5000蚊10日"},{"pid":"1278ed2462c25da119c5017aea82bfe4964b2a86","tid":387660,"uid":95413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T05:38:42.000Z","msg":"上年玩10定唔知11日 連機票酒店都係萬1萬2蚊多d<br />\n不過我同班朋友對食無要求  行街行到肚餓就求撚其指一間就入去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n住就頭一星期蚊型酒店(定民宿 唔知算唔算)  <br />\n乾淨整齊 價錢唔記得  不過算平  環境都幾舒服<br />\n行去大久保站都係10分鐘內<br />\n<br />\n最後幾日去左富士山個邊間垃圾飯店  <br />\n又貴又污糟  冷氣重熱撚過閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最貴個餐我記得都係食左4000yen到<br />\n個陣無話特別就住d錢黎用  不過洗幾多錢睇人既姐<br />\n你瘋狂買野既話  最少帶2萬5啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91eb873aaf920388d44764f8e8d63fa8be4a5a06","tid":387660,"uid":63202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply