quote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n未預到用幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  btw 我預多因為我同條女會狂食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 早午晚便利店宵夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以15000 係for 2個人定 每人$15000？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩人呀</blockquote><br />\n唔買手信應該ok ，一日三餐，平平地兩個3000円一餐，14日都要12萬yen 加埋交通應該差唔多，你仲要沖繩去福岡呢⋯⋯</blockquote><br />\n計哂交通住宿 15000淨係食同玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  福岡去沖繩搭ana 想去百合之濱</blockquote><br />\n百合之濱真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上年4月去過不過要夾岩退潮時間<br />\n同埋個島都無咩好玩好食又細 係來回個島最貴<br />\n不過十分值得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打 介唔介意加我tg講多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  tg:sadsad6863</blockquote><br />\n其實我都講唔到多d你聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 主要我朋友plan<br />\n我係鹿兒島坐船去仲要隔日先一班船 （有飛機不過幾貴）<br />\n你plan之前google check下百合之濱個時間先<br />\n一年都唔係成日有 如果天氣唔好又唔出得海<br />\n真係要天時地理人和我覺得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就同朋友島上住民宿住左幾日<br />\n老闆仲會車我地去玩同睇下個島<br />\n但係個島一日一夜都行哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd3b59ac2448618efdbed36deea4f0b067030b1","tid":387660,"uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T23:38:09.000Z","msg":"得期五你想去乞食?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇13萬唔洗去，平均一日一萬係基本"},{"pid":"0905bfe7ea25efddf1536bc4c62004dae12baed4","tid":387660,"uid":120955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T00:15:42.000Z","msg":"預10萬港幣"},{"pid":"5f2630da5e30ace8daa96aa7259bf68461679b06","tid":387660,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":1